Title: Danfoss modulating actuator 24v
Description: The Danfoss AME130 modulating actuator is suitable for use with fan coil units, induction units, small re-heaters and re-coolers and in zone applications where hot or cold water is the controlled medium. Easy to install, this actuator requires no tools for mounting and promises a lifetime free of maintenance costs.

Title: DANFOSS AMV 435 24V 3-POINT ACTUATOR
Description: Incorporating load-related switch-off, the advanced Danfoss AMV 435 actuator is capable of ensuring that actuators and valves are safe from the risk of overload. Ideal for use with VRB, VRG, VF and VL type two and three-way valves up to DN80 and with AHQM DN size DN40 to DN100, the AMV 435 is also compatible with DN40 to DN100 AB-QM pressure independent balancing and control valves.

Title: Belimo LRF rotary actuator 230v
Description: Suitable for ball valve use, the Belimo LRF 230V rotary actuator offers 4Nm actuating torque. Tensioning a return spring when moving the valve to its operational position, the actuator will return the valve to its fail-safe position using the same spring if the voltage supply is interrupted.
